metadata.description:
Many thanks to all my friends, 
who support my art despite the trends. 
For all who read the description 
Until it ends. 

To the friends who still love me
When my mental health is wearing thin.
To the new friends who don’t know me
This message is for you too. 

You are loved by the world
I hope you never feel blue. 

On times that we are down
And feel there is no hope. 
This little appreciation token
Should help us all cope. 

With love on my birthday to you,
 EddieLee21 𝙾𝚍𝚎 𝚝𝚘 𝙰𝚛𝚒𝚎𝚜
